body:
This is v1.18.0 Release Candidate 2.

Key changes:
* Fixed some memory leaks.
* Fixed a use-after-free (potential crashing) bug when closing qTox while in an audio/video call.
* Preliminary Android 7 support. The UI doesn't work well on Android at all. Contributions welcome.
* Removed ASCII versions of smiley packs. Feedback on the need for these or similar features is welcome.

Please check if there are [issues](https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/issues) that aren't planned for the [v1.18.0 milestone](https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/milestone/1) that you think should be in it, and let us know if so.

As always, please report any issues you find with this pre-release.

## What's Changed
* chore: Add modern interactive issue template. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/169
* fix: Typo fix unavaliable -> unavailable. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/176
* chore: Make About -> File bug link use the new form-based bug report. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/181
* docs: Translations update from Hosted Weblate by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/177
* chore: Add a debug build for Android APK. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/182
* docs: Translations update from Hosted Weblate by @weblate in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/168
* chore: Set min sdk version to 24 (Android 7). by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/173
* chore: Don't build Qt stuff in bazel cross-compile builds. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/184
* cleanup: Another typo fix, avaliable -> available. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/178
* cleanup: Use tox core "length" functions instead of constants. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/174
* docs: Add TokTok/qTox adoption to the about form. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/190
* cleanup: Remove most of the leftovers from toxext. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/186
* cleanup: Remove now unused DESKTOP_NOTIFICATIONS from cmake preset. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/189
* chore: Point weblate config at the new hosted weblate project. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/183
* fix: Fix use-after-free when closing qTox during a call. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/192
* cleanup: Avoid logging QString as format. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/122
* cleanup: Prefix multi-line log messages with the same timestamp. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/199
* cleanup: Some random warning cleanups and some typo fixes. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/198
* test: Make the invalid proxy test less flaky. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/197
* chore: Use `mkstamp` macro to get git version from bazel build. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/202
* chore: Enable rtti in all builds. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/204
* fix: Fix two memory leaks. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/205
* fix: cmake file dependencies by @Monsterovich in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/206
* docs: Translations update from Hosted Weblate by @weblate in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/203
* cleanup: Use consistent nomenclature for "macOS". by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/212
* docs: Translations update from Hosted Weblate by @weblate in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/216
* cleanup: Stop loading smileypack in a separate thread. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/215
* chore: Add arm64 macOS user build. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/211
* cleanup: Sort Qt resource files by filename. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/214
* chore: Add UBSAN option for cmake. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/193
* chore: Reduce default number of PR CI builds. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/221
* chore: Don't run non-deploy jobs on push (only PR). by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/223
* cleanup: Reduce repetition in Android build workflow. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/222
* chore: Fix nightly apk upload. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/224
* chore: Add armeabi-v7a build. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/219
* chore: Use qt_binary instead of cc_binary for qtox. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/201
* feat: Add caps-lock indicator in password edit on macOS. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/213
* chore: Add ccache to most builds. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/225
* cleanup: Use consistent nomenclature for "full screen". by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/210
* test: Re-enable tests on windows. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/154
* chore: Add fully static qtox build. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/227
* cleanup: Avoid double spaces in logging. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/226
* chore: Build windows outputs into arch-specific build dirs. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/228
* refactor: Remove the need for `<filesystem>` in logging. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/229
* fix: Show actual smileys in the smileypack selector. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/231
* cleanup: Remove duplicate definition of DECLARE_SIGNAL. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/235
* cleanup: Remove ASCII versions of smiley packs. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/233
* fix: Use the *last* `/src/` to find the source root. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/237
* chore: Don't imgbot-optimise SVGs. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/241
* docs: Add some more context to the "filing an issue" section. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/242
* chore: Fix ccache cache sharing. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/243
* docs: Translations update from Hosted Weblate by @weblate in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/244
* perf: Delay debug log loading to show time. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/238
* chore: Don't build Debug builds on release tag pushes. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/245

## New Contributors
* @Monsterovich made their first contribution in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/206

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/compare/v1.17.90...v1.18.0-rc.2
